{
  "id": "adv_event_2502_01_02",
  "title": "秘密の\nチョコレート",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――二月十三日バレンタインデー前日、ライブ会場にて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—February 13th‚ the day before Valentine’s Day‚ at the live venue",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐサニピのライブが始まる時間だな\n……ん？　みんなで集まって何をしているんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s almost time for Sunny Peace’s live to start.\n…Hmm? What are they all gathered together doing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8333334208,
      "endTime": 11.2141725778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.4075056632
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、材料は私が用意しておくから\n今夜、寮のキッチンに集合でいいわね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then I’ll prepare the ingredients‚\nso let’s meet in the dorm kitchen tonight‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.4075056632,
      "endTime": 17.633197267699998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.8331971724
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "分かった……手作りするのは初めてだけど……\n頑張って挑戦してみる……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Got it… it’s my first time making them by hand‚ but…\nI’ll do my best and give it a try…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.8331971724,
      "endTime": 24.346235616900003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.5529020547
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "みんなと一緒に心を込めて手作りするよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll put my heart into making them together with everyone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.5529020547,
      "endTime": 28.6269611119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.8269611596
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "手作りってなんの話だ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Making… what are you talking about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.8269611596,
      "endTime": 31.2867345094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.4800678808
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ、{user}さん！？\nいつからそこに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh—{user}-san!?\nHow long have you been there?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.4800678808,
      "endTime": 35.199999999999996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.3878388165
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今来たばかりだが……ひょっとして、みんなで\nバレンタインのチョコを手作りするって話か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just got here… could it be that you’re all\ntalking about making Valentine chocolates together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.3878388165,
      "endTime": 42.757543826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.9442103783
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "ううっ……バレた……\n驚かせようと思って秘密にしてたのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… he figured it out…\nWe wanted to keep it a secret and surprise you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.9442103783,
      "endTime": 48.767112867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.9737795908
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃあ、明日はバレンタインだし分かるよ\nでも安心してくれ。誰にも言ったりしないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ tomorrow is Valentine’s Day‚ so I can guess.\nBut don’t worry—I won’t tell anyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.9737795908,
      "endTime": 56.4911720354,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.6845051208
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "サプライズでみんなから手作りチョコをもらえたら\n明日の仕事のスタッフさん達もきっと喜んでくれるさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If the staff get handmade chocolates from all of you as a surprise‚\nI’m sure they’ll be happy at tomorrow’s job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.6845051208,
      "endTime": 63.9006504455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.0873171884
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "え？　もしかして、スタッフに配る義理チョコの話を\nしてると思ってる……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Does he think we’re talking about\nobligation chocolates for the staff…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.0873171884,
      "endTime": 71.89482308209999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.0948229867
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん静かに！　そ、そうなのよ～！　この時期は\n仕事関係で義理チョコを配ることが多くて大変なのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan‚ shh! Y-yes‚ that’s right~! Around this time‚\nit’s tough because we have to give out lots of obligation chocolates for work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.0948229867,
      "endTime": 83.1310359078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに気を遣わなくてもいいと思いますよ\n市販のチョコを買って渡すだけでも十分……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t think you need to worry that much.\nSimply giving store-bought chocolates would be enough…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.3376993892,
      "endTime": 89.720647311,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.8539787052
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "ダメです！　それだと気持ちがちゃんと伝わりません！\n私にとってこのチョコレートは大事なものなんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No! That wouldn’t properly convey our feelings!\nThese chocolates are really important to me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.8539787052,
      "endTime": 98.22893750649999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.4356040397
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "そう……渡すのなら、ちゃんと……私の想いを沢山\n込めたチョコを贈りたい……そうじゃないと意味がない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right… if I’m going to give them‚ then I want to give\nchocolates filled with all my feelings… otherwise there’s no point.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.4356040397,
      "endTime": 108.0556943337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.2690273999
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（なんだかみんなの反応が変だな。やけに真面目だし）\n（スタッフにあげる義理チョコの話じゃないのか……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Something feels off about everyone’s reactions. They’re unusually serious.）\n（Is this not about obligation chocolates for the staff…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.2690273999,
      "endTime": 118.06381175509999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.2571452219
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（も、も、もしかして、義理じゃない……本命チョコ？）\n（ま、まさか、恋人！？　そんな相手がいたのか！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（C-c-could it be… not obligation chocolates… but real ones?）\n（N-no way… a lover!? They have someone like that!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.2571452219,
      "endTime": 129.9092312891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.102564756
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（いや、片思いということも……もしかしたら悪い男に）\n（騙されて……ああ、相手は一体誰なんだ……！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（No‚ maybe it’s unrequited love… or maybe some bad guy）\n（tricked them… ahh‚ who on earth is it…!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.102564756,
      "endTime": 139.2725646416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.4792311747
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "ほ、ほらみんな、そろそろライブが始まる時間よ\n早くステージに行かないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "L-look‚ everyone‚ it’s almost time for the live to start.\nWe need to head to the stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.4792311747,
      "endTime": 146.16682749580002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.2735000371
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "そうね！　{user}君、また後で！\nさくらちゃん、いつものやつ、今日は超特急でお願い",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right! {user}-kun‚ see you later!\nSakura-chan‚ the usual one—today‚ full speed ahead‚ please.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.2735000371,
      "endTime": 154.3681033849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.5547699372
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "うん、分かったよ！\n太陽の光と共にサニーピース！　さ、行こ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ got it!\nWith the sunlight‚ Sunny Peace! Alright‚ let’s go!",
        "id": ""
      },
